{"id":1661,"date":"2024-08-23T21:05:29","date_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:05:29","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1661"},"modified":"2024-08-23T21:05:29","modified_gmt":"2024-08-23T21:05:29","slug":"aerodactylite","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/","title":{"rendered":"Aerodactylite"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table grey left\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"big center text-large\">Aerodactylite (Mega Stone)<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Location<\/th>\n<td>Found inside the puzzle room in Crystal Peak.<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Mega Evolution<\/th>\n<td>Aerodactyl<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<h2>Prerequisites<\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Have access to Crystal Peak<\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm08-rock-climb\/\">Rock Climb<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm03-surf\/\">Surf<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Have <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/tms-hms\/hm06-rock-smash\/\">Rock Smash<\/a><\/li>\n<li>Defeat the Elite 4 to access the crystal switches<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Location<\/h2>\n<p>Enter Crystal Peak and follow the linear path going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/01-pokemon-unbound-following-the-path-forward-in-crystal-peak.jpg\" alt=\"Following the path forward in Crystal Peak. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Following the path forward in Crystal Peak.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Smash the breakable rocks blocking your path and use the ladder behind them to go deeper into the cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/02-pokemon-unbound-using-the-ladder-to-go-down.jpg\" alt=\"Using the ladder to go down. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using the ladder to go down.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Surf to continue going forward.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/03-pokemon-unbound-using-surf-to-continue-forward.jpg\" alt=\"Using Surf to continue forward. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Surf to continue forward.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Turn north to reach the area with interactable crystals.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/04-pokemon-unbound-surfing-toward-the-area-with-interactable-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Surfing toward the area with interactable crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Disable the yellow and red crystals, ensuring only the blue crystals are activated.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/05-pokemon-unbound-disabling-the-red-and-yellow-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Disabling the red and yellow crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Disabling the red and yellow crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With the interactable crystal part done, backtrack and take the ladder deeper into the mountain.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/06-pokemon-unbound-climbing-the-ladder-to-the-upper-floor.jpg\" alt=\"Climbing the ladder to the upper floor. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Climbing the ladder to the upper floor.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Use Rock Climb to scale the south wall before following the path west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/07-pokemon-unbound-using-rock-climb-to-go-down-then-following-the-path-west.jpg\" alt=\"Using Rock Climb to go down, then following the path west. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Using Rock Climb to go down, then following the path west.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Continue on the path until you see a blue switch. Interact with it to disable the blue crystals.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/08-pokemon-unbound-disabling-the-blue-crystals.jpg\" alt=\"Disabling the blue crystals. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Disabling the blue crystals.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Disabling the crystals will allow you to continue south where you\u2019ll see the entrance to a small room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/09-pokemon-unbound-entering-the-puzzle-room.jpg\" alt=\"Entering the puzzle room. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Entering the puzzle room.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Aerodactylite is inside the small room.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/mega-stones\/aerodactylite\/10-pokemon-unbound-finding-the-aerodactylite.jpg\" alt=\"Finding the Aerodactylite. \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Finding the Aerodactylite.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/mega-stones\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/mega-stone-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">Mega Stones<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1662,"parent":278,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[12],"class_list":["post-1661","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-mega-stones"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1661","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/278"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1662"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1661"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1661"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}